        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">What nobody tells medical practices about websites</p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Dentist: "Patients book, then no-show" - website 2015, PDF appointment form, broken mobile</p>
