            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Doctor bios with photos + "Why I Practice": 47% more new patient bookings</p>
