        <li><strong>Appointment booking</strong> - Easy scheduling without phone calls</li>
        <li><strong>Doctor/staff profiles</strong> - Credentials, specialties, photos</li>
        <li><strong>Service information</strong> - Treatments, procedures, what to expect</li>
        <li><strong>Patient resources</strong> - Forms, insurance info, FAQ</li>
        <li><strong>HIPAA considerations</strong> - Patient data handling</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Medical Website Testing Results</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
