      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I use AI builders for HIPAA-compliant medical sites?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">You can use AI builders for the public-facing parts of your medical site (services, doctor profiles, general info). For patient data storage, booking systems, and any PHI (protected health information), you need HIPAA-compliant third-party tools integrated with your site.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Which AI builder is best for solo doctors?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Durable AI is ideal for solo practitioners. You can have a complete site with appointment booking in under 5 minutes total investment. The built-in CRM helps track patient follow-ups.</p>
